'''2017年中國大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2017 Chinese Grand Prix}}），官方名稱為'''2017年一級方程式賽車海尼根中國大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2017 Formula 1 Heineken Chinese Grand Prix}}）<ref name="official"/>，是2017年4月9日舉辦於[[中國|中國]]的一場[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]賽事。比賽在[[上海國際賽道|上海國際賽道]]進行，總計56圈。這是[[2017年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2017年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的第2場分站賽事，<ref name="prov. calendar">{{cite web|url=http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-4|title=FIA Announces World Motorsports Council decisions|accessdate=2016-11-30|author=|date=2016-11-30|publisher=Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130174153/http://www.fia.com/news/fia-announces-world-motor-sport-council-decisions-4|archive-date=2016-11-30|access-date=|deadurl=no}}</ref>以及第14屆[[中國大獎賽|中國大獎賽]]。

醫療直升機因為上海的天候因素，無法在20分鐘內完成救護任務，使得週五練習賽的進行不甚順遂。[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]在中國大獎賽取得他跨季連續第6座桿位，[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]與[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]則以第2及第3位發車。正賽在賽道濕滑但沒降雨的狀態下展開，漢米爾頓自起跑後一路領先至比賽結束，並且拿下最快單圈紀錄。維泰爾在虛擬安全車期間進站將半雨胎更換為光頭胎，一度下滑至第6名，最終仍重返原先的發車名次取得亞軍。本日最佳車手[[馬克斯·維斯塔潘|馬克斯·維斯塔潘]]從第16位發車，首圈便超越9輛車，最高曾來到第2名，最終取得季軍。

== 賽事簡報 ==

=== 自由練習賽 ===
週五兩階段的自由練習賽皆受到低雲、降雨及濃霧等氣候因素影響。第一階段在賽道濕滑的狀態下進行，再加上紅旗的部署，整場練習賽僅進行了20分鐘。<ref name="BBCgrounded">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/formula1/39524299|title=Second practice called off after safety helicopter grounded|last=Benson|first=Andrew|date=2017-04-07|work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407074631/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/formula1/39524299|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據安全規則，無論是透過直升機或救護車，傷及神經的車手必須在20分鐘內送達醫院。<ref name="SkyF1reschedule">{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828102/chinese-gp-could-be-rescheduled-due-to-weather-concerns-in-shanghai|title=Chinese GP format to be unchanged despite Shanghai weather concerns|last=|first=|date=2017-04-07|work=|newspaper=[[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409021232/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828102/chinese-gp-could-be-rescheduled-due-to-weather-concerns-in-shanghai|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時的天氣狀態下，醫療直升機不可能在距離賽道38公里遠的醫院降落，救護車亦無法在時間內抵達醫院，因此，直到緊急醫療運輸能夠執行前，車輛將禁止上賽道練習。天氣狀況依舊沒有改善，第二階段練習賽也被迫取消。<ref name="BBCgrounded" /><ref name="GallowaySkyF1">{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10823260/chinese-gp-practice-one-low-cloud-restricts-early-running-in-shanghai|title=Chinese GP Practice: Heavy cloud restricts Friday running in Shanghai|last=Galloway|first=James|date=2017-04-07|work=|newspaper=[[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408013714/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10823260/chinese-gp-practice-one-low-cloud-restricts-early-running-in-shanghai|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]希望改期以讓整個比賽週末能順利執行，但是，官方認為這會打亂原定的電視播出，且將對一週後[[2017年巴林大獎賽|巴林賽事]]的後勤帶來重大影響，而將他訴求駁回。<ref name="SkyF1reschedule" /><ref name="GallowaySkyF1" />包括漢米爾頓及積分領先者[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]在內的部分車手皆未在週五上場，[[馬克斯·維斯塔潘|馬克斯·維斯塔潘]]在賽道潮濕的狀態下，以1:50.491的時間寫下週五最快成績。<ref name="GallowaySkyF1" />第二階段練習賽期間，漢米爾頓獲允許穿越賽道與車迷互動，並將自己的簽名帽丟向主看台的群眾；他利用社群媒體建議一級方程式賽車的新老闆，這樣的狀況將為他帶來「主動發揮創意」的機會。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39526963|title=Chinese Grand Prix: Hamilton calls for race weekend changes after Shanghai cancellation|last=Benson|first=Andrew|date=2017-04-07|newspaper=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407115109/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39526963|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828220/lewis-hamilton-meets-the-fans-during-chinese-gp-practice-delays|title=Lewis Hamilton meets the fans during Chinese GP practice delays|last=|first=|date=2017-04-07|work=|newspaper=[[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407235056/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828220/lewis-hamilton-meets-the-fans-during-chinese-gp-practice-delays|dead-url=no}}</ref>像是開放闈場讓在場車迷參觀等的應急方案也相繼被提出，以預防如同此次練習賽被取消的突發狀況。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/f1-urged-to-create-contingency-plan-after-practice-cancellation-890664/|title=F1 urged to create "contingency plan" after practice cancellation|last=Anderson|first=Ben|date=2017-04-07|work=|publisher=Motorsport Network|newspaper=motorsport.com|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409020930/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/f1-urged-to-create-contingency-plan-after-practice-cancellation-890664/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

週六的天氣由濕轉乾，<ref name = BBCFP3 />第三階段練賽如期展開，各車隊實際上僅執行了三分之一的練習賽，對於排位賽的準備將是嚴峻的考驗。大多數的車隊選擇讓自家車手分別測試不同的輪胎，進而蒐集一些跑長距離的數據，以利用這唯一的機會為下午的排位賽做準備。<ref name = F1.comFP3>{{cite news|title = FP3 – Ferrari set searing Shanghai pace|url = https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/headlines/2017/4/fp3---ferrari-edge-ahead-in-shanghai.html|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08|website = [[formula1.com|formula1.com]]|publisher = [[Formula_One_World_Championship|Formula One World Championship]] Limited|archive-date = 2017-04-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170408180400/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/headlines/2017/4/fp3---ferrari-edge-ahead-in-shanghai.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>天氣預報預測週日有很大的機率會降雨，<ref name = BBCFP3 />使得車隊在此練習賽中的數據計算增添了額外的難題。[[印度威力車隊|印度威力]]透過[[Twitter|Twitter]]形容：「週六上午從沒來有如此重要過。」<ref>{{cite tweet|user = ForceIndiaF1|number = 850557423207239680|title = Time for FP3! Never has the Saturday morning session been so important - 60 minutes to get all data we need for qualifying! #ChineseGP|author = Sahara Force India|authorlink = Force India|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08}}</ref>維泰爾以1:33.336的成績寫下此階段練習賽的最快圈速，與隊友[[奇米·雷克南|奇米·雷克南]]僅相差0.053秒；<ref name = FP3times>{{cite web|title = 2017 Formula 1 Heineken Chinese Grand Prix – Practice 3|url = https://www.formula1.com/en/results.html/2017/races/960/china.html|website = [[formula1.com|formula1.com]]|publisher = [[Formula_One_World_Championship|Formula One World Championship]] Limited|accessdate = 2017-04-08|date = 2017-04-08|archive-date = 2017-04-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170407151429/https://www.formula1.com/en/results.html/2017/races/960/china.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name = SkyFP3 />他們兩位寫下的成績皆比[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]在[[2016年中國大獎賽|2016年]]的[[桿位|桿位]]時間（1:35.402）快上2秒。<ref>{{cite web|title = 2016 Formula 1 Pirelli Chinese Grand Prix – Qualifying|url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2016-race-results/2016-china-results/qualifying.html|website = [[formula1.com|formula1.com]]|publisher = [[Formula_One_World_Championship|Formula One World Championship]] Limited|accessdate = 2016-04-16|date = 2016-04-16|archivedate = 2016-04-16|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160416140244/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2016-race-results/2016-china-results/qualifying.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>兩位梅賽德斯車手以0.3至0.5秒之差落後法拉利雙雄，儘管漢米爾頓曾在前兩區段與維泰爾持平，但他仍在最後的髮夾彎發生失誤。[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]因為車輛的「T型翼」斷裂，在最後一彎跑開而喪失時間。<ref name = SkyFP3 />其餘的車手皆落後領先集團1秒以上，[[費利佩·馬薩|費利佩·馬薩]]以1:34.773的成績取得第5名，<ref name = FP3times />領先後方的兩位[[紅牛車隊|紅牛]]車手。<ref name = SkyFP3 />紅牛很早便以重油載領先全場，但隨後的排位賽模擬卻無法追趕上法拉利及梅賽德斯。<ref>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP: Vettel fastest as Ferrari sets stunning pace in FP3|first = Andrew|last = van Leeuwen|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/chinese-gp-vettel-fastest-as-ferrari-sets-stunning-pace-in-fp3-890927/|newspaper = motorsport.com|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409021321/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/chinese-gp-vettel-fastest-as-ferrari-sets-stunning-pace-in-fp3-890927/|dead-url = no}}</ref>紅牛後方的競爭就顯得更加激烈，8至10名的車手（[[蘭斯·斯托爾|蘭斯·斯托爾]]、[[喬里昂·帕爾默|喬里昂·帕爾默]]及[[小卡洛斯·塞恩斯|小卡洛斯·塞恩斯]]）間僅相差0.041秒，<ref name = FP3times />而11至16名的車手（[[尼可·賀根堡|尼可·賀根堡]]、[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]、[[塞吉歐·培瑞茲|塞吉歐·培瑞茲]]、[[羅曼·格羅斯讓|羅曼·格羅斯讓]]、[[丹尼爾·科維亞特|丹尼爾·科維亞特]]及[[埃斯特班·奧康|埃斯特班·奧康]]）則相距0.362秒。<ref name = F1.comFP3 />兩屆世界冠軍[[費爾南多·阿隆索|費爾南多·阿隆索]]及[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫車隊]]僅能以本田引擎差勁的性能、穩定性及油耗，在時間表末端與[[薩伯車隊|薩伯]]爭奪名次，<ref name = BBCFP3>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP: Sebastian Vettel on top in final practice as Ferraris outshine Mercedes|first = Andrew|last = Benson|newspaper = [[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39537316|archive-date = 2017-04-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170408062813/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39537316|dead-url = no}}</ref>落後最快車手超過2.5秒。<ref name = SkyFP3 />

=== 排位賽 ===
[[天空體育F1台|天空體育F1台]]預測法拉利在排位賽將會較梅賽德斯具有優勢，且兩支車隊將自成一個集團，<ref name = SkyFP3>{{cite news|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828485/chinese-gp-practice-three-sebastian-vettel-tops-ferrari-one-two|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08|title = Chinese GP Practice Three: Sebastian Vettel tops Ferrari one-two|first = Pete|last = Gill|newspaper = [[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409021313/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828485/chinese-gp-practice-three-sebastian-vettel-tops-ferrari-one-two|dead-url = no}}</ref>這項預測也成功被證實了。<ref name = SkyQualiRep />維泰爾在第一階段排位賽以1:33.078取得最快成績，領先第2的漢米爾頓約0.25秒，位居第3的雷克南則與漢米爾頓相差僅0.01秒，<ref name = QresultFIA />然而，法拉利使用的是軟胎而梅賽德斯則是較快的超軟胎。在三階段排位賽中，紅牛的[[丹尼爾·里卡多|丹尼爾·里卡多]]是其餘車手中表現最佳的，但也與最快車手相差1秒以上，可見的是紅牛將自身降格，<ref>{{cite news|newspaper = [[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|title = Conclusions from Chinese GP Qualifying: What we learnt|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828486/conclusions-from-chinese-gp-qualifying-what-we-learnt|first = James|last = Galloway|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|archive-date = 2017-04-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170408221159/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828486/conclusions-from-chinese-gp-qualifying-what-we-learnt|dead-url = no}}</ref>且在[[2017年澳洲大獎賽|澳洲]]較前兩支車隊缺乏速度並非單一事件。<ref name = SkyQualiRep /><ref name = RBRquali />

第一階段排位賽初期，[[哈斯車隊|哈斯]]車手羅曼·格羅斯讓於最後一彎發生打滑，他設法讓車輛不去撞牆，順利帶著磨損的輪胎回到維修站。薩伯車手[[安東尼奧·焦維納齊|安東尼奧·焦維納齊]]就沒有如此幸運了，當他暫居第15位時，在最後一彎跑上人工草皮打滑，車輛重重地撞上牆並回彈至賽道中央。<ref>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP 2017 Qualifying: Antonio Giovinazzi crashes out|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|newspaper = [[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828489/chinese-gp-2017-qualifying-antonio-giovinazzi-crashes-out|archive-date = 2017-04-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170408221219/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828489/chinese-gp-2017-qualifying-antonio-giovinazzi-crashes-out|dead-url = no}}</ref>賽會因為這起事故在起跑大直道部署雙黃旗，任何車手皆無法再刷新自己的成績，焦維納齊雖然挺進第二階段，但因為車輛已經損壞，僅以第15名結束排位賽。帕爾默及格羅斯讓兩位在第一階段被淘汰的車手，在焦維納齊事故發生後仍試圖免於被淘汰的命運，隨後遭判罰退5個發車位；賽會幹事稱他們「在雙黃旗區段沒有明顯減速的意圖」。<ref name = 5place />格羅斯讓則對這項判決提出質疑，在Twitter上發佈當時的遙測數據，顯示他在彎角處提前50公尺剎車，並以每小時45公里的低速駛過該路段，<ref>{{cite tweet|number = 850666277400170496|user = RGrosjean|author = Romain Grosjean|authorlink = Romain Grosjean|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|title = So apppatently I made no effort to slow down and didn't abandon the lap... data shows a different point of view. Btw didn't even open my DRS}}</ref>但賽會幹事依舊維持原判。<ref name = 5place />哈斯車隊老闆[[京特·施泰納|京特·施泰納]]表示對格羅斯讓的支持，認為他已經明確地減速，對於格羅斯讓喪失進入第三階段的機會趕到嘆息。<ref>{{cite news|title = Haas boss "doesn't get" Grosjean's yellow flag penalty|first = Glenn|last = Freeman|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/haas-boss-doesn-t-get-grosjean-s-yellow-flag-penalty-891237/|newspaper = motorsport.com|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409111610/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/haas-boss-doesn-t-get-grosjean-s-yellow-flag-penalty-891237/|dead-url = no}}</ref>焦維納齊車輛的維修必定需要一具全新的變速箱，使得他的排位因罰退下降至第18位，將從最後一排的格羅斯讓及帕爾默前頭發車。<ref name = GiovinazziGearbox/>

紅牛的維斯塔潘面臨引擎不點火的問題，直到第一階段末期才寫下排位時間，落後位居第5的隊友1.5秒。維斯塔潘試著刷新時間，結果因為焦維納齊的撞車，以第19位遭到淘汰，正賽時將從第17位發車。<ref name = RBRquali>{{cite news|title = Verstappen blames engine misfire for Q1 exit|first = Edd|last = Straw|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/verstappen-blames-engine-misfire-for-q1-exit-891154/|newspaper = motorsport.com|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409200151/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/verstappen-blames-engine-misfire-for-q1-exit-891154/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

到了第二階段排位賽，維泰爾在初期便寫下最快圈速，用上同樣輪胎的漢米爾頓僅落後0.015秒。雷克南在末期寫下1:32.181的最快圈速，領先其隊友0.21秒，<ref name = QresultFIA />並超越[[麥可·舒馬克|麥可·舒馬克]]在2004年創下的賽道紀錄。<ref name = SkyQualiRep>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP Qualifying: Lewis Hamilton claims Shanghai pole|first = James|last = Galloway|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828101/chinese-gp-qualifying-lewis-hamilton-claims-shanghai-pole|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409201523/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828101/chinese-gp-qualifying-lewis-hamilton-claims-shanghai-pole|dead-url = no}}</ref>位居第5的里卡多與第4名的鮑達斯相差1秒以上。兩位梅賽德斯車手及里卡多是場上唯一只做出一次圈時的車手。賀根堡及培瑞茲在最後一刻刷新成績，順利挺進第三階段，進而讓塞恩斯、埃里克森、馬格努森及阿隆索遭到淘汰。<ref name = SkyQualiRep />

漢米爾頓在第三階段的首圈表現不如預期，但仍以1:31.902的成績保持領先，維泰爾以0.184秒之差取得第2位，鮑達斯位居第3。雷克南的時間落後漢米爾頓0.7秒，不過依舊領先第5名的里卡多。隨後，前四名車手皆刷新自身的時間，但名次並未更動。漢米爾頓的新單圈時間為1:31.678，維泰爾寫下的1:31.864僅與鮑達斯相差0.001秒，雷克南的1:32.140則較里卡多快上約0.9秒。<ref name = SkyQualiRep /><ref name = QresultFIA />第6名的馬薩與紅牛相距約半秒，並領先[[雷諾車隊|雷諾]]的賀根堡。[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯]]車手蘭斯·斯托爾在生涯第二場一級方程式賽事便首度挺進第三階段，取得第10名，比初登場時的第19名進步許多。他的進步部分可歸功於較輕的動力輔助轉向設定——斯托爾曾在沒有動力輔助轉向的狀態下贏得2016年[[歐洲三級方程式錦標賽|歐洲三級方程式錦標賽]]，且他認為採取一些錯誤的決定是讓一級方程式賽車進步的必然因子。<ref>{{cite news|title = Stroll boosted by switch to lighter power steering|first = Edd|last = Straw|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-09|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/stroll-boosted-by-switch-to-lighter-power-steering-891241/|newspaper = motorsport.com|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409111929/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/stroll-boosted-by-switch-to-lighter-power-steering-891241/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

漢米爾頓取得他自[[2016年美國大獎賽|2016年美國大獎賽]]開始的跨季連續第6座桿位，在[[一級方程式賽車車手紀錄列表#最長連續桿位|最長連續桿位]]紀錄排行榜暫居第6位。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/consecutive.aspx|accessdate = 2017-04-09|website = statsF1.com|title = Pole positions – consecutively|archive-date = 2015-09-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920093505/http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/consecutive.aspx|dead-url = no}}</ref>這也是他在[[中國大獎賽|中國大獎賽]]的第6座桿位，在[[一級方程式賽車車手紀錄列表#最長連續桿位|同一場大獎賽最多桿位]]紀錄排行榜暫居第5位。<ref name = SkyQualiRep /><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/grandprix.aspx|accessdate = 2017-04-09|website = statsF1.com|title = Pole positions – by Grand Prix|archive-date = 2015-05-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150528011108/http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/pole/grandprix.aspx|dead-url = no}}</ref>同時也是梅賽德斯在150場完賽中的第75座桿位。

=== 正賽 ===
國際汽聯採取措施確保緊急醫療能夠執行，預防如同週五練習賽受到影響的情形再度發生。警方將提供護送以加快陸地運輸，神經學專門設備也被搬遷至距離賽道5公里的醫院。<ref>{{cite news|title = FIA takes steps to ensure Chinese GP will run on time|first = Adam|last = Cooper|date = 2017-04-08|accessdate = 2017-04-08|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/fia-takes-steps-to-ensure-chinese-gp-will-run-on-time-890911/|newspaper = motorsport.com|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409021241/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/fia-takes-steps-to-ensure-chinese-gp-will-run-on-time-890911/|dead-url = no}}</ref>其中，包含安排一支[[華山醫院|華山醫院]]神經外科醫療團隊週日至[[瑞金醫院|瑞金醫院]]出診，瑞金醫院不僅在各種天氣狀態下交通方便，還能夠提供所需的醫療服務。<ref>{{cite news|newspaper = Autosport|title = Chinese GP: FIA makes special arrangements at nearby hospital|first = Jonathan|last = Noble|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/128875/fia-makes-special-hospital-arrangements|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409201346/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/128875/fia-makes-special-hospital-arrangements|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

正賽當日早晨有著相當多的降雨，<ref name = BBCreport />但是比賽在標準程序下展開。除了用上光頭胎的塞恩斯以外，所有車手皆選擇以半雨胎發車。維泰爾因為起跑前停超出車格被調查，最終沒有受到任何懲處。維斯塔潘在首圈超越9輛車，賽後獲選為「本日最佳車手」。<ref name = BBCreport /><ref>{{cite news|title = Max Verstappen named Driver of the Day for Chinese GP|url = https://www.motorsportweek.com/news/id/14267|newspaper = Motorsport Week|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-10|first = Jack|last = Leslie|archive-date = 2017-04-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170410214324/https://www.motorsportweek.com/news/id/14267|dead-url = yes}}</ref>前幾圈內，培瑞茲與斯托爾的碰撞事故造成斯托爾衝進碎石堆，賽會隨後部署虛擬安全車，維泰爾在此時進站換上光頭胎。<ref name = FIAreport>{{cite news|title = F1 – Hamilton wins Chinese Grand Prix ahead of Vettel and Verstappen|url = http://www.fia.com/news/f1-hamilton-wins-chinese-grand-prix-ahead-vettel-and-verstappen|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|work = FIA.com|publisher = [[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]]|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409200730/http://www.fia.com/news/f1-hamilton-wins-chinese-grand-prix-ahead-vettel-and-verstappen|dead-url = no}}</ref>不久後，焦維納齊在起跑線直道上發生嚴重撞車事故，帶出了安全車，大多數的車手選擇進站更換光頭胎。<ref name = MS.comReport>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP: Hamilton wins as wet start causes fireworks|first = Valentin|last = Khorounzhiy|website = motorsport.com|url = https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/chinese-gp-hamilton-wins-as-wet-start-causes-fireworks-891570/|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|publisher = Motorsport Network|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409200501/https://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/chinese-gp-hamilton-wins-as-wet-start-causes-fireworks-891570/|dead-url = no}}</ref>賀根堡因為在虛擬安全車狀態下超越格羅斯讓，被判罰5秒加時，接著又因為在安全車時超車埃里克森，再受罰10秒加時。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2017/04/09/hulkenberg-given-two-penalties-safety-car-errors/|title = Hulkenberg given two penalties for Safety Car errors|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|first = Keith|last = Collantine|website = f1fanatic.co.uk|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409202830/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2017/04/09/hulkenberg-given-two-penalties-safety-car-errors/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>鮑達斯犯下一個自認愚蠢的失誤，他在跟隨安全車時，為了保持輪胎溫度發生打滑，下滑至第12名，並遭到他的車隊老闆及前經理[[托托·沃爾夫|托托·沃爾夫]]指責。<ref>{{cite news|title = Chinese Grand Prix: Valtteri Bottas says spin under safety car was 'stupid mistake'|first = Andrew|last = Benson|newspaper = [[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-10|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39545283|archive-date = 2017-04-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170410134302/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39545283|dead-url = no}}</ref>

安全車回到維修站後，漢米爾頓保持領先地位，里卡多及上演一系列超車鏡頭的維斯塔潘緊追在後，兩輛法拉利則位居4、5名。<ref name = SkyReport>{{cite news|title = Chinese GP: Lewis Hamilton and Mercedes back to winning ways|first = James|last = Galloway|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828494/chinese-gp-lewis-hamilton-and-mercedes-back-to-winning-ways|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-09|newspaper = [[Sky_Sports_F1|Sky Sports F1]]|archive-date = 2017-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409201122/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10828494/chinese-gp-lewis-hamilton-and-mercedes-back-to-winning-ways|dead-url = no}}</ref>從第16位發車的維斯塔潘在第11圈超車里卡多，上到第2名，再度證明他在潮濕天氣下的驚人技巧（如同[[2016年巴西大獎賽|2016年巴西大獎賽]]）。隨著法拉利依舊無法超越里卡多，漢米爾頓及維斯塔潘的領先持續擴大。<ref name = MS.comReport />第20圈時，維泰爾超越了隊友雷克南，此時，漢米爾頓與維斯塔潘差距4秒，與里卡多相差9秒。 兩圈後，維泰爾超車里卡多並迅速拉近與維斯塔潘的差距。<ref name = FIAreport />到了第27圈，漢米爾頓將領先擴大至8.5秒，維斯塔潘則與維泰爾相差1.5秒，後方的里卡多及雷克南分別落後維泰爾2及4秒。維斯塔潘在第29圈發生鎖死失誤，將第2名讓給了維泰爾。<ref name = SkyReport />比賽剩下27圈，漢米爾頓保有10.6秒的領先。維斯塔潘在下一圈進站換上全新的超軟胎，<ref name = FIAreport />重返賽道後落後鮑達斯，暫居第6名。
換上新胎的維斯塔潘展現出絕佳的速度，很快地便超越鮑達斯，也讓持續落後漢米爾頓的維泰爾趕緊進站。漢米爾頓在第37圈進站，以全新的軟胎重返賽場，出站後落在雷克南前方。儘管雷克南反覆抱怨輪胎問題，但他卻是前6名車手中最後進站的。<ref name = FIAreport />第42圈，前5名車手為漢米爾頓、維泰爾、維斯塔潘、里卡多及雷克南。兩輛紅牛在最後幾圈互相爭搶頒獎台的最後一個席位，最終，里卡多沒能超越他的隊友。<ref name = MS.comReport />名次在最後15圈皆不曾在變動，鮑達斯重回第6名，<ref name = BBCreport />塞恩斯、馬格努森、培瑞茲及奧康成功在積分圈內完賽。漢米爾頓在這場大獎賽取得一級方程式賽車生涯第54座分站冠軍，第5座中國大獎賽冠軍<ref name = FIAreport />（曾在[[2008年中國大獎賽|2008]]、[[2011年中國大獎賽|2011]]、[[2014年中國大獎賽|2014]]及[[2015年中國大獎賽|2015年]]奪冠），以及梅賽德斯150場完賽中的第65場冠軍。由於漢米爾頓取得冠軍而維泰爾位居亞軍，兩者在2017年積分榜上以43分持平，梅賽德斯則在車隊積分榜上超越法拉利。<ref name = SkyReport />漢米爾頓在第44圈以1:35.378的時間拿下本場的最快圈速紀錄，<ref name = FIAresults />較尼可·羅斯堡在2016年寫下的1:39.824快上4秒之多。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.fia.com/file/40470/download?token=4VDVV5Zr|title = 2016 Chinese Grand Prix Race – Official Classification|date = 2016-04-16|accessdate = 2017-04-09|work = FIA.com|publisher = [[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]]|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160417121908/http://www.fia.com/file/40470/download?token=4VDVV5Zr|archive-date = 2016-04-17|dead-url = no}}</ref>漢米爾頓成為繼舒馬克之後，第2位在3條賽道各贏得5座以上冠軍的車手，並追平[[亞倫·保魯斯|亞倫·保魯斯]]的生涯106場頒獎台完賽紀錄，<ref name = BBCreport>{{cite news|title = Lewis Hamilton wins Chinese Grand Prix ahead of Sebastian Vettel|newspaper = [[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-10|first = Andrew|last = Benson|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39538689|archive-date = 2017-04-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170410134309/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/39538689|dead-url = no}}</ref>在[[一級方程式賽車車手紀錄列表#總頒獎台完賽數|生涯頒獎台完賽]]排行榜上名列第2。<ref>{{cite web|title = Podiums by number|url = http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/podium/nombre.aspx|website = statsf1.com|date = 2017-04-09|accessdate = 2017-04-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409213216/http://www.statsf1.com/en/statistiques/pilote/podium/nombre.aspx|archive-date = 2017-04-09|dead-url = yes}}</ref>這場比賽是漢米爾頓繼[[2014年馬來西亞大獎賽|2014年馬來西亞]]及[[2015年義大利大獎賽|2015年義大利]]大獎賽後，第3場「[[一級方程式賽車車手紀錄列表#桿位、分站冠軍、最快圈速及領跑每一圈|大滿貫]]」（桿位起跑一路領先至奪冠並拿下最快圈速）勝利。漢米爾頓同時也追平[[吉姆·克拉克|吉姆·克拉克]]的11場「帽子戲法」（桿位起跑奪冠並拿下最快圈速）紀錄，在這項紀錄的[[一級方程式賽車車手紀錄列表#同場賽事中拔桿、奪冠及最快圈速|排行榜]]上名列第2。

